      "title": "[Boing Boing] The theory that UFOs come from Earth, not space",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F19%2Fcryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F19%2Fcryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F19%2Fcryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F19%2Fcryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F19%2Fcryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/19/cryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"The theory that UFOs come from Earth, not space\"><img alt=\"cryptoterrestrial hypothesis — U.S. National Archives (NAID 303938034) / Public domain (via Wikimedia Commons)\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"561\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Flying_Saucer_-_NARA_NAID_303938034_cropped-1.png?fit=894%2C561&amp;quality=55&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"894\" /></a><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Most UFO theories reach for outer space. The <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptoterrestrial_hypothesis\">cryptoterrestrial hypothesis</a> reaches down instead: it proposes that flying saucers come not from distant planets but from an advanced, hidden civilization that has been living on Earth all along — under the oceans, inside mountains, or beneath our feet. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/19/cryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/19/cryptoterrestrial-hypothesis.html\">The theory that UFOs come from Earth, not space</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
